::Cyclonus think for awhile. Speedbreaker had a point::
Cyclonus: Hmm.
:He looks around. They were four::
Cyclonus: We can manage, yes.
::He pauses for a second, but his thoughts are cut short by hearing Angel 
Prime's shouting::
Cyclonus: Damn! Kill him!
::Cyclonus flies toward Angel Prime fires 4 high powered laser blasts at him::
~~~~~
::Scourge fires 25 rapid laser blasts at Angel Prime::
~~~~~
::My Destrons were watching Cygnar. Ramjet could not beleive his eyes. the 
base was gone::
Ramjet: You are not the last Destrons. I am Ramjet, leader of the Destrocons. 
These are my team members: Dirge, Skywarp, Falcon, and Snare. We have been 
loyal Destrons for a long time. What has happened here?
~~~~~
::Time Warp walked into the cave, curled up into one corner, and fell asleep::
